{"tid":1198503,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"11號晚11點 立會見","createTime":"2019-06-10T09:00:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-10T09:50:44.000Z","uid":23993,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"c6b0fb8268e716f880be599162b595b175cfe67d","tid":1198503,"uid":23993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T09:00:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dKLoAt9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdKLoAt9.png&h=57e6bc62&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n我知經過尋晚之後 肯放低身段帶頭衝被塔嗰班 告士打道俾速龍趕埋牆角投降嗰班 未必再可以出嚟<br />\n但你甘心咩？甘心再一次輸得一敗塗地咩？<br />\n再一次輸俾呢個蠻橫無理 全港8分1嘅人口100萬人上街都可以當你冇到嘅極權咩？<br />\n我唔甘心呀 我要贏呀屌佢老母 哪怕事後幾多鬼呀收咗錢呀一句句一刀刀插埋嚟 我就係想贏番次<br />\n話掂都係要佢撤 做乜仲要等大會照開<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>一定要係二讀前就做嘢<br />\n等民陣嗰班搞得嚟 都過咗啦戇鳩<br />\n<br />\n唔好再設多餘嘅心理關口俾自己 唔肯整污糟雙手 就乜柒都冇<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">Don't cry to quit! <br />\nYou already in pain, you already hurt! <br />\nGET A REWARD FROM IT!</span> </strong></span>"},{"pid":"9d197fef13d25160a2349af0101559fcaef8285c","tid":1198503,"uid":23993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T09:02:13.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"5912742b3a09e8fce80e0cc42bfc6d41ced0d870","tid":1198503,"uid":23993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T09:02:24.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"f71bf1e79f1e9e4a43639b79018e12ae9c92a211","tid":1198503,"uid":23993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T09:04:00.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"701d044dfee5e48ef5e952ccab50011a00b6f0d2","tid":1198503,"uid":23993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T09:04:58.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"cfd6e37615fd1dfef34c494101b6ad9f642faf41","tid":1198503,"uid":47879,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T09:05:10.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"081b1c130cc8e0f5405bd003a8ea128b93024ef6","tid":1198503,"uid":23993,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T09:10:37.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>唔夠人嘅話<br />\n今次行動形同自殺<br />\n但我會唔會去？<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">會！！！</span><br />\n我敢打賭 我唔會係唯一一個<br />\n見到呢個po嘅手足 請用你哋嘅方法 將呢個消息廣傳開去 求吓你哋<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong></span>"},{"pid":"7e25f18e2f9ab10c383dcb082288dfde4467f30f","tid":1198503,"uid":154486,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T09:11:44.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/FNl5HyhhWwg&nbsp;\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FFNl5HyhhWwg%C2%A0&d=AePTNAtL1N4PdcNq2S6jCGWYsxP5Z0Wle18NOkmjjC4%3D&h=a8130cfd\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/FNl5HyhhWwg&nbsp;</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n吾友奮起 血戰沙場<br />\n由桑水到頓河<br />\n茫茫我土 昭昭吾國<br />\n他人不可侵犯<br />\n<br />\n鮮血遍地 魂魄飛逝&nbsp;<br />\n全為吾等自由<br />\n以此足證 吾等兄弟<br />\n皆為哥薩克民族！"},{"pid":"1e697ea8ced7b09f5173ef54d75def019804b52a","tid":1198503,"uid":23993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T09:12:40.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"27fcba37de339084dce3c63768de177cb1bf01b7","tid":1198503,"uid":23993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T09:14:17.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"2c16c4641bb9eb0e4dddb2ca77aa31978605aada","tid":1198503,"uid":23993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T09:15:54.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"914904a407d6c4c72ddcb4d1cda13c58a425b111","tid":1198503,"uid":23993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T09:17:24.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"f75053a6b1f02c2465b6fde39f596c6b1a2e9ac3","tid":1198503,"uid":23993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T09:18:15.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"f605b07cc4827b82bb60b199111e91a0d11e7158","tid":1198503,"uid":23993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T09:19:09.000Z","msg":"求幫推"},{"pid":"90cbdcde1d564294edda37ae60709beb5a89b403","tid":1198503,"uid":23993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cit